Dialogue: 10,0:00:00.39,0:00:02.73,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:06.11,0:00:06.94,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:06.94,0:00:08.65,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Your leg is a wreck.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:08.65,0:00:12.61,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I know, but what else am I supposed to do? It's all I've got.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:12.61,0:00:15.32,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Better bring my crutch, just to be safe.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:15.32,0:00:19.66,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,But I told you I'd be your leg for you!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:19.66,0:00:23.29,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,No, thank you. Besides, I never asked for that, anyway.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:25.62,0:00:27.38,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,What's got you so pouty?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:27.38,0:00:28.49,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Oh, nothing.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:28.49,0:00:31.71,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Just jealous of how you rely on your leg so much
Dialogue: 10,0:00:31.71,0:00:33.88,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,that you'll use it until it's dinged and scratched all over.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:33.88,0:00:34.80,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:34.80,0:00:41.56,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Losing to a bundle of sticks and joints besmirches my good name as a robot.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:41.56,0:00:45.69,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I have to prove that me and my high specs are more useful!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:45.69,0:00:47.15,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Natsuki-san, I-
Dialogue: 10,0:00:47.15,0:00:48.02,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:48.02,0:00:50.02,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I haven't even said anything yet!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:50.02,0:00:53.74,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Don't you dare get any funny ideas, got it?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:53.74,0:00:55.99,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:57.91,0:00:59.16,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,You coming, or what?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:59.16,0:01:00.58,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Where are you...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:00.87,0:01:02.45,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,We're going to school now, aren't we?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:02.45,0:01:05.58,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,You're coming, too?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:06.54,0:01:09.96,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Wait for me! I have to be your leg!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:42.89,0:02:44.22,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,You're gonna want this.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:44.22,0:02:45.68,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Gotta take notes in class.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:47.56,0:02:50.85,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Thank you! Now I can keep logs!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:51.40,0:02:52.15,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Keep what?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:52.15,0:02:58.36,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Logs! Nonko told me to keep them so I could have a record of what happened on any given day.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:58.36,0:02:59.61,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Sounds low-tech.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:59.61,0:03:02.16,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Can't you just store that information in your memory?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:02.16,0:03:03.66,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I can.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:03.66,0:03:07.45,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,But apparently this is supposed to help me develop more human-like memory storage faculties.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:08.04,0:03:11.08,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Maybe you losing your memories
Dialogue: 10,0:03:11.08,0:03:14.75,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,was an intentional effort to make you feel more human.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:15.63,0:03:18.38,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,You're so smart, Natsuki-san! You got it in one!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:18.38,0:03:21.76,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,QED! My memory loss is proof positive of my astronomically high-
Dialogue: 10,0:03:21.76,0:03:23.18,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Slow down there, speed racer.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:24.14,0:03:27.39,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,, "Going to school with Natsuki-san." That's all?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:28.35,0:03:33.35,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,No peeking! That's in violation of the Robot Privacy Act!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:36.73,0:03:38.32,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Welp.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:38.32,0:03:39.69,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,We just have to cross!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:39.69,0:03:43.16,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,With my incredible jumping abilities, I can clear this gap with-
Dialogue: 10,0:03:43.16,0:03:43.95,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I don't think so.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:43.95,0:03:45.20,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:45.70,0:03:48.16,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,If you swim, you'll get dirty.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:48.16,0:03:49.20,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Not what I mean.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:49.20,0:03:52.46,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,People go to school every day, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:52.46,0:03:54.08,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I'm sure there's some way to-
Dialogue: 10,0:03:54.08,0:03:55.42,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,Hold it right there!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:56.92,0:03:58.92,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,What in the world!?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:58.92,0:04:01.34,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,You're not going anywhere, hitman!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:01.34,0:04:02.38,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Hitman?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:02.38,0:04:04.34,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,We know all about you!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:04.34,0:04:07.43,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,You're an evil hired gun from the mainland, aren't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:07.43,0:04:08.97,Default,Miyo,0,0,0,,We've heard the stories.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:08.97,0:04:13.10,Default,Miyo,0,0,0,,You have a rifle hidden in your crutch, and you're not afraid to use it!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:13.10,0:04:16.52,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Oh. That's the game we're playing, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:16.98,0:04:20.53,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,If you wanna hurt Natsuki-san, you'll have to go through me first!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:20.53,0:04:21.74,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,Back off, loser!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:21.74,0:04:22.74,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Loser!?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:22.74,0:04:24.15,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,You heard her, loser.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:24.15,0:04:25.95,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Not you too!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:26.49,0:04:30.74,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I've got very important business at your school.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:30.74,0:04:34.12,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,If you don't want a piping-hot rifle round for lunch, you'd better stay out of my way.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:35.00,0:04:37.54,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,Ririka, what do we do?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:37.54,0:04:40.34,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,T-Tactical retreat! Run for it!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:40.96,0:04:42.34,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,After 'em, Atri.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:42.34,0:04:43.01,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:43.01,0:04:44.05,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Hurry up.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:06.99,0:05:07.95,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,You'll never catch me alive!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:09.66,0:05:11.58,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I thought I was supposed to be the bad guy.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:11.58,0:05:13.45,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,We have to follow them!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:14.79,0:05:20.09,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,With my incredible jumping abilities, I can clear this gap with-
Dialogue: 10,0:05:21.50,0:05:22.80,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:22.80,0:05:23.51,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:28.89,0:05:30.76,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,Ririka, look!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:31.26,0:05:33.43,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,Aaah, I forgot!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:36.73,0:05:38.65,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Okay, let's go.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:45.19,0:05:46.49,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Looking pretty barren.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:49.41,0:05:50.37,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,He's here!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:50.37,0:05:51.74,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,There they are.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:53.45,0:05:56.87,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,All right, everyone! It's time for class!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:56.87,0:05:58.12,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Minamo?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:59.33,0:06:01.50,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Take your seats.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:01.50,0:06:02.59,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,Minamo-chan!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:02.59,0:06:04.67,Default,Miyo,0,0,0,,We've got trouble! The hitman's here!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:04.67,0:06:05.84,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,Run for your life!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:05.84,0:06:07.01,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Hitman?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:08.26,0:06:09.05,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Freeze!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:10.84,0:06:11.89,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Natsu-kun!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:11.89,0:06:13.18,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,Natsu-kun?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:13.18,0:06:15.14,Default,Miyo,0,0,0,,Isn't he the hitman? And-
Dialogue: 10,0:06:15.14,0:06:15.68,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,The loser!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:16.23,0:06:17.73,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I'm not a loser!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:17.73,0:06:20.73,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Yeah. She's got a name,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:20.73,0:06:23.32,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,and it's Bootleg Humanoid McToaster the Third, Esquire.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:23.32,0:06:24.32,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,You mean Atri!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:24.32,0:06:25.94,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,You really came!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:26.28,0:06:29.32,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I'm leaving once class starts, though.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:29.32,0:06:30.20,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Where's the teacher?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:31.03,0:06:32.16,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:32.49,0:06:34.41,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,You're real clueless, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:34.41,0:06:36.29,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,Minamo-chan's our teacher!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:36.29,0:06:39.83,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,She teaches us language arts, math, science, social studies, everything!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:40.17,0:06:40.96,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,You're the teacher?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:40.96,0:06:45.25,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Yeah. All the real ones evacuated to the mainland.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:45.25,0:06:47.88,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,And there's hardly any students left, too...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:50.01,0:06:53.18,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,My dad wants me to do the paperwork to shut the school down
Dialogue: 10,0:06:53.18,0:06:55.64,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,and transfer to the mainland.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:55.64,0:06:58.77,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,It sure doesn't look like it's functioning as a school.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:58.77,0:06:59.64,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:00.27,0:07:04.36,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,We don't even have electricity, so we can only have class when it's bright out.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:04.36,0:07:06.48,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,That's no environment to educate kids in.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:06.78,0:07:08.28,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,You can do what you want,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:08.28,0:07:12.36,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,but you really should send these kids to the mainland so they can get a decent education.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:12.70,0:07:16.29,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,They have aid programs for disaster victims, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:16.29,0:07:19.87,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,Shut up. You don't know what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:21.17,0:07:22.17,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Ryuu-chan!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:22.17,0:07:26.88,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,What would you know? You're just a fancy-pants elite who abandoned his home to go to the Academy on the mainland.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:26.88,0:07:29.17,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I didn't abandon anything.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:29.17,0:07:33.09,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I studied hard and went to the Academy so I could make a difference.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:33.09,0:07:33.93,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,That's all there is to it.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:33.93,0:07:35.55,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,Then let's see that difference.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:37.31,0:07:40.27,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,Ever since you came back, you've been shutting yourself up in your boat.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:40.27,0:07:42.19,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,At least we're actually making an effort.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:42.19,0:07:43.19,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Ryuu-chan!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:43.19,0:07:45.23,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,You sound just like the mainlanders.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:45.23,0:07:48.73,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,You talk a big game with all your idealism, and then you sit on your ass.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:48.73,0:07:50.82,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,You leave the rest of us to suffer.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:56.91,0:08:00.04,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Heave-ho! Heave-ho!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:00.04,0:08:03.25,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,Bye, Atri! See you tomorrow!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:03.25,0:08:07.46,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Bye! See you all tomorrow!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:07.88,0:08:09.92,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Looks like you've made some friends, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:09.92,0:08:14.18,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Yes. School's a much more fun place than I was expecting.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:14.68,0:08:16.64,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,What were you expecting?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:17.14,0:08:21.10,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I had a feeling school was a very sad place.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:21.52,0:08:24.02,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Oh, that's ridiculous. Right?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:26.27,0:08:29.36,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Sorry. I should've stayed home.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:29.36,0:08:31.94,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,No, you didn't do anything wrong.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:32.32,0:08:34.66,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,I'm sure Ryuu-chan knows that, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:34.66,0:08:37.74,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,He just had a bad experience on the mainland, that's all.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:37.74,0:08:38.62,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,He did?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:38.99,0:08:45.00,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Yeah. Those kids lost their parents, so he tried taking them to the mainland once,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:45.00,0:08:48.50,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,but, you know, they're struggling, too,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:48.92,0:08:52.92,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,so the kids ended up getting ostracized at school.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:55.30,0:08:58.43,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Natsuki-san looks sad.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:58.43,0:09:01.31,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Yeah. Cheer him up when you get home, okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:01.31,0:09:04.31,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Me? Of course!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:06.98,0:09:08.06,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,You know, Natsu-kun,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:08.61,0:09:13.07,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,I'd really appreciate it if you came back tomorrow.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:13.07,0:09:14.74,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,What's the point?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:14.74,0:09:17.53,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Not like there's anything for you to teach me.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:17.53,0:09:21.20,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Yeah, but there's plenty for you to teach us.{Technically ambiguous. She could also be saying there's stuff she CAN teach him (contrasting with his "I don't NEED anything), but considering how the episode turns out, I think this interpretation is more likely.}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:24.91,0:09:26.21,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I'll think about it.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:28.25,0:09:29.92,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Hey, where's Atri?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:29.92,0:09:33.51,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,She said she was going on ahead. You gave her permission.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:33.51,0:09:35.88,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Huh? Oh, right.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:35.88,0:09:37.88,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,She said she wants to get ready to cheer you up.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:38.22,0:09:39.64,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Cheer me up?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:40.68,0:09:41.76,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:42.22,0:09:45.14,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,It's okay! You don't have to panjc!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:45.14,0:09:49.27,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,I'm sure she just wants to make a nice dinner for you and-
Dialogue: 10,0:09:51.94,0:09:52.98,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Uh-oh.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:55.40,0:09:56.45,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Atri!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:58.41,0:10:00.62,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Welcome home, Natsuki-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:00.62,0:10:05.45,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Huh? I can't see... I can't see!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:06.58,0:10:07.66,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,What's all this?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:07.66,0:10:14.21,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I, uh, I thought you might like it if I made you a tasty dinner...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:14.21,0:10:17.13,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,How does cooking turn into this mess?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:17.13,0:10:21.39,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,W-Well, as I've said before, in a way, making human-like mistakes
Dialogue: 10,0:10:21.39,0:10:24.47,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,is actually proof of my stupendously high-
Dialogue: 10,0:10:24.47,0:10:26.73,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,No human screws up this bad.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:26.73,0:10:28.85,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Maybe something's malfunctioning?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:28.85,0:10:29.60,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:29.60,0:10:33.10,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,It's possible. But I don't have any way to repair her, is the problem.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:33.10,0:10:35.19,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Guess I'd better chuck her back into the sea.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:35.19,0:10:36.53,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:36.53,0:10:38.95,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Then how do you explain this catastrophe?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:38.95,0:10:41.28,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,U-Uh, that's easy...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:42.78,0:10:44.20,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Actually...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:44.20,0:10:45.45,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Actually?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:45.45,0:10:50.71,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Actually, I'm a top-secret combat robot developed by a foreign government.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:50.71,0:10:52.00,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:52.33,0:10:56.76,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Yes. I came to this country to take it down from the inside...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:02.68,0:11:05.89,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,But the war came to an end before I could carry out my mission.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:07.14,0:11:11.90,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I lost not only my homeland, but my very purpose in life.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:13.27,0:11:17.65,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,All of a sudden, I was a poor, lonely killing machine with nowhere to go.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:18.11,0:11:22.11,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,But in my time of despair, Nonko took me in.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:23.12,0:11:26.41,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,She gave me a name,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:26.41,0:11:29.87,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,and she gave me a new purpose.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:30.62,0:11:31.67,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,And that was...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:31.67,0:11:33.04,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Housework...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:33.04,0:11:36.96,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Exactly. But as a combat unit,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:36.96,0:11:38.59,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I find it difficult to control my own power.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:38.59,0:11:39.21,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Atri.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:39.21,0:11:39.80,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:39.80,0:11:42.05,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Humanoids can lie?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:42.05,0:11:44.01,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Yes! Of course!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:44.01,0:11:46.68,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I'm high-spec, baby!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:47.56,0:11:49.68,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,You were lying!?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:52.35,0:11:56.02,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Don't you think this breaks the Humanoid Abuse Act?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:56.02,0:11:58.53,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,She doesn't need food. She'll be fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:58.53,0:12:02.74,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,If you ask me, a robot lying to its master is a {\i1}much{\i0} bigger problem.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:02.74,0:12:04.41,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I beg to differ!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:04.41,0:12:06.87,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,One, I am a robot.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:06.87,0:12:08.79,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Two, I am poor at housework.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:08.79,0:12:14.29,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,From these two immutable facts, simple deductive reasoning leads to the eminently logical conclusion
Dialogue: 10,0:12:14.29,0:12:16.92,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,that I very well may be-
Dialogue: 10,0:12:16.92,0:12:18.84,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Then let's see some combat.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:18.84,0:12:21.59,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,A war machine like you's gotta at least have missiles, yeah?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:21.59,0:12:24.18,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,O-Of course!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:24.18,0:12:25.47,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Rocket pun-
Dialogue: 10,0:12:30.18,0:12:31.81,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,On second thought, I'd better not.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:31.81,0:12:36.40,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I have to obey the Three Laws of Robotics, and I can hardly guarantee your life.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:36.40,0:12:39.40,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,You live to see another day, Natsuki-san.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:39.69,0:12:41.82,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Why is sass the one thing you're good at?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:42.24,0:12:44.03,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Because of my high-
Dialogue: 10,0:12:44.03,0:12:44.99,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:46.95,0:12:51.12,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,You know, Atri-chan, I think you've cheered Natsu-kun up.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:51.12,0:12:52.37,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Really!?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:52.37,0:12:54.41,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Here, come eat with us.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:54.41,0:12:56.58,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,You'll love this tamagoyaki.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:59.96,0:13:00.71,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Don't waste our food!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:01.09,0:13:03.72,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Tres bien!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:03.72,0:13:05.09,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I swear...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:07.84,0:13:11.10,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,See you two tomorrow!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:11.47,0:13:13.98,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I'm looking forward to lunch!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:13.98,0:13:16.10,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Nobody said you'd be eating any!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:16.10,0:13:19.56,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I can perceive flavor and distinguish between good ones and bad ones.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:19.56,0:13:23.19,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,A feat only made possible by my downright preposterous specs!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:23.19,0:13:25.78,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Oh, I'd better keep my logs...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:26.28,0:13:27.53,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:27.99,0:13:29.83,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:29.83,0:13:31.24,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,It's gone.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:31.24,0:13:32.04,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:32.04,0:13:37.00,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I think I left my notebook at school!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:43.80,0:13:45.55,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Can't this wait until tomorrow?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:45.55,0:13:50.05,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Absolutely not. Logs are of vital importance!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:50.05,0:13:52.31,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,You'd think you wouldn't forget it, then.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:55.64,0:13:57.19,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Boy, it's dark.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:57.19,0:13:58.23,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Nighttime generally is.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:58.23,0:14:00.48,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,That's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:02.98,0:14:04.86,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,What the heck is that?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:05.28,0:14:08.03,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Are you scared, Natsuki-san?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:08.03,0:14:12.20,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,N-No! That was totally weird, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:12.20,0:14:14.20,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,We don't have electricity on this island.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:14.20,0:14:17.66,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Aw, are you a widdle scaredy-cat?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:17.66,0:14:19.00,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Poor baby.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:19.00,0:14:23.80,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I remember when you got so scared, you clung to me in your sleep!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:23.80,0:14:27.01,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Ooh, you're just too precious!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:29.51,0:14:34.01,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Wait! We can talk this out, Natsuki-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:36.89,0:14:41.44,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,It's flooded with seawater. It was fine earlier...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:41.86,0:14:44.07,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,High tide...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:44.07,0:14:47.44,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Of course. {\i1}That's{\i0} why there's nothing on the second floor.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:51.45,0:14:54.28,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,There really is something up there...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:55.70,0:14:58.04,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I've picked it up in high-sensitivity mode!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:58.04,0:15:00.25,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,It's a person! I'mma go see!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:00.25,0:15:02.33,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Hey! Atri!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:03.08,0:15:04.71,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Hey, Atri?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:05.25,0:15:06.30,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Atri...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:10.01,0:15:11.84,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Found it!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:13.97,0:15:15.81,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,So, what about the light?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:16.10,0:15:18.31,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,There was nobody there.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:18.31,0:15:20.10,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,You said you saw a person.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:20.10,0:15:23.40,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,What if it was a... ghooooost?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:24.77,0:15:25.73,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Knock it off.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:25.73,0:15:27.90,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,They might've gone upstairs.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:30.24,0:15:31.91,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Didn't know you can access the roof.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:31.91,0:15:34.28,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Looks like nobody's here.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:34.82,0:15:37.24,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Think it was a ghooooost?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:37.24,0:15:39.79,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,You're a robot. Stick to science.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:39.79,0:15:40.91,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:41.37,0:15:42.17,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:44.38,0:15:46.80,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,That's the one! I'm sure of it!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:46.80,0:15:48.51,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Wh-Who's there?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:50.01,0:15:51.05,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,Huh? The hitman?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:51.05,0:15:52.09,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:56.35,0:15:58.10,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,Hey, it {\i1}is{\i0}you.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:58.43,0:15:59.89,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Ririka!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:59.89,0:16:01.89,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,What're you doing here?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:01.89,0:16:05.90,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,What do you mean? I live here, stupid.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:05.90,0:16:08.32,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,What? You do?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:08.32,0:16:12.20,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,Not just me, either. Ryuu-chan and Tooru, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:12.20,0:16:14.61,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,Their houses sunk into the sea.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:15.82,0:16:18.33,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,Guess I need wind, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:18.74,0:16:21.79,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,And I was almost done with this book, too...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:24.00,0:16:25.13,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,You're generating electricity...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:25.13,0:16:30.13,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,I've got nothing better to do at night, so I borrow this from the library.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:30.13,0:16:33.30,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,I figure maybe I'll find a way to bring electricity back to the island.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:35.39,0:16:36.22,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:37.35,0:16:38.64,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Ryuuji?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:40.02,0:16:42.35,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,What're you doing here, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:43.39,0:16:45.60,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,Here. 'S not much, but I got some snacks for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:45.60,0:16:48.52,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,Thanks! How about batteries?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:49.19,0:16:51.78,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,Sorry. I looked all over and couldn't find any.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:52.11,0:16:55.16,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,Oh. Thanks anyway!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:56.66,0:16:59.37,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,Don't strain yourself to read that, okay? It's bad for your eyes.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:59.87,0:17:00.91,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,Get some sleep.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:01.33,0:17:02.16,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:05.08,0:17:06.67,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,This is how it is for us.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:08.54,0:17:10.21,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,Those of us who have nothing,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:10.21,0:17:13.38,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,we get kicked off the mainland before we can accomplish anything.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:13.38,0:17:16.97,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,But the people who already have something, they get whatever they want.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:17.55,0:17:21.31,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,We want to study so we can change something, but we don't even get to do that much.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:55.47,0:17:57.43,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Guess it's worth a shot.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:00.55,0:18:03.43,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Natsuki-san! Where were you?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:03.43,0:18:07.73,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Hey, when you're done with that, can you spin the turbine outside?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:07.73,0:18:11.06,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Sure, but why?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:11.06,0:18:13.40,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I have an idea I wanna test.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:16.15,0:18:17.82,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:17.82,0:18:19.61,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Yeah, go for it!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:31.38,0:18:33.38,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Are you done yet?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:33.38,0:18:34.63,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Gimme some more!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:34.63,0:18:36.38,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:38.13,0:18:40.97,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Put your back into it! You're a combat robot, aren't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:42.39,0:18:46.64,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Ngh, you sure do know how to run a robot ragged...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:47.18,0:18:50.73,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Looks like it's too small to give me anything in the way of efficiency.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:50.73,0:18:54.15,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,But a big one would come with its own problems...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:58.24,0:18:59.53,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:59.53,0:19:03.40,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Natsuki-san, can I stop yet?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:03.40,0:19:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Natsuki-saaan...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:06.79,0:19:08.50,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Natsuki-san?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:16.38,0:19:19.42,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Natsuki-san, you dirty boy...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:23.64,0:19:26.01,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Natsuki-san? Huh!?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:26.01,0:19:27.60,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Oh, you're up.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:27.60,0:19:29.48,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Get ready fast, or we're gonna be late.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:29.48,0:19:32.48,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Have you been working all night long?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:32.85,0:19:36.61,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Sure. At the Academy, we called it "Tuesday."
Dialogue: 10,0:19:36.61,0:19:39.53,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Anyway, I'm bringing something for show-and-tell today.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:39.53,0:19:40.65,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Can you carry it for me?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:42.53,0:19:44.91,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,You're coming to school?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:46.16,0:19:46.99,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:49.66,0:19:56.13,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,All right, class, I've invited a special guest lecturer today for a one-of-a-kind lesson!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:56.13,0:19:57.80,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,A guest lecturer?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:57.80,0:19:58.34,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:58.34,0:20:00.26,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Come in!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:04.39,0:20:05.47,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,Oh. It's you.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:05.47,0:20:07.43,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Keep your disappointment to yourself!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:07.43,0:20:08.81,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,It really hurts, you know.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:12.35,0:20:13.48,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:13.85,0:20:17.44,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Some stuff I scrounged up around town last night.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:17.44,0:20:22.40,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,A lightbulb, a motor, a pinwheel, and a dry cell.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:22.78,0:20:24.24,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,Aw, what?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:24.24,0:20:26.78,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,That ain't gonna last long without wind, genius.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:27.12,0:20:28.62,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Sure won't.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:28.62,0:20:31.20,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,That's why it gets thrown out with the trash,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:31.20,0:20:34.12,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,even on this island, where we need everything we can get.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:34.12,0:20:38.29,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,But even junk like this has its uses...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:41.55,0:20:43.80,Default,Miyo,0,0,0,,It's so bright!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:43.80,0:20:45.80,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,Yeah, when it's windy out.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:45.80,0:20:50.93,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Right. But what if we could store the electricity we're generating?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:00.02,0:21:03.61,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,No way! You can store wind energy?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:03.61,0:21:05.24,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Depends on how you go about it, but yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:05.24,0:21:06.99,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,You want a medal or something?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:06.99,0:21:08.45,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Ryuu-chan...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:08.45,0:21:12.79,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,There's only so much electricity a tiny little pinwheel like that can produce.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:12.79,0:21:14.50,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,Stop getting their hopes up.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:14.83,0:21:18.00,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,That's a good point. But what if it wasn't tiny?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:18.42,0:21:22.38,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,You better not tell me you're gonna build a giant turbine.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:22.38,0:21:24.17,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,You really think you can do that?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:24.17,0:21:25.97,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Is it really out of the question?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:25.97,0:21:29.51,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Besides, wind isn't the only way to generate electricity.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:29.51,0:21:34.68,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,There's thermal power, water power, nuclear power, geothermal power, and not to mention...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:35.52,0:21:37.06,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,The sea?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:37.06,0:21:39.02,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,You can make electricity with the sea?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:39.36,0:21:43.15,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Yeah. Lucky for us, this school is sitting right in it,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:43.15,0:21:46.53,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,and the second floor gets flooded at high tide.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:47.45,0:21:48.95,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,We can use that power.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:48.95,0:21:50.20,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Natsu-kun!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:50.20,0:21:52.24,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,Get real, man!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:52.24,0:21:54.12,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,What about materials, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:54.12,0:21:56.66,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,Anything this island had is already-
Dialogue: 10,0:21:57.04,0:21:57.83,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Right here.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:57.83,0:21:59.04,Default,Ryuuji,0,0,0,,There's a treasure trove of goodies
Dialogue: 10,0:22:00.54,0:22:05.55,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,{=5}ripe for the taking!
